    "Puis nous bougeons à l’unisson, chaque partie de nos corps ne faisant qu’un."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:243
translate french mari12b_f4010c57:

    # "It's the closest I've ever felt to her."
    "Je ne me suis jamais senti aussi proche d’elle."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:247
translate french mari12b_e219a86e:

    # "And when we cum together, I feel everything that she feels."
    "Et quand on jouit ensemble, je ressens tout ce qu’elle ressent."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:248
translate french mari12b_e721ecdf:

    # "We hold each other close as I empty myself into her."
    "On se serre l’un contre l’autre pendant que je me vide en elle."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:251
translate french mari12b_743db198:

